{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"apothecial-commodious-canary","description":"## Summary\n\nWith the ALLOW_MODEL_REQUESTS session-guard fix landed (Gerrit 442), the external\n'external integration (live services)' job now runs its live tests (17 pass) instead of\nfailing every one at the model call. That unmasked 3 pre-existing failures — tests not\nupdated for src design changes landed after the suite last passed (2026-06-16):\n\n1. **test_ref_lock_ac0_live.py::test_ac0_blob_ref_roundtrips_through_real_origin** —\n   `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'rebar_reconciler'` at _ref_lock.py:249. The test\n   loads _ref_lock.py by file path and never puts src/rebar/_engine on sys.path; the\n   reconciler git-op refactor (d9e0f0e7, 2026-07-07) added `from rebar_reconciler import\n   git_adapter`. Sibling external tests already add ENGINE_DIR to sys.path.\n\n2. **test_pydantic_ai_cutover_live.py::test_pydantic_text_mode** — `RuntimeError: agentic\n   filesystem tools attempted OUTSIDE the repo-snapshot gate` (config.py:228). The\n   direct-runner RunRequest defaults to execution_mode='agentic', which trips the\n   snapshot-gate safeguard added in b25fafcd1 (2026-06-27). A text reply needs no fs tools.\n\n3. **test_pydantic_ai_cutover_live.py::test_pydantic_review_code** — `assert\n   'code-review-disabled' == 'pydantic_ai'`. review_code became an off-by-default 4-pass\n   gate (2d3e7611a, 2026-07-01); the old assertion tests a removed contract. Decision:\n   enable the gate and validate the live gated path (runner == 'code-review-gate').\n\nAll three are test-only fixes (no src defect); confined to test_ref_lock_ac0_live.py and\ntest_pydantic_ai_cutover_live.py.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n\n1. Trigger the external-integration workflow (external job) on main.\n2. Observe: 3 failed, 17 passed, 8 skipped — the 3 failures above.\n\nExpected: the external job is green.\nActual: 3 stale live tests fail.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] test_ref_lock_ac0_live puts src/rebar/_engine on sys.path so `from rebar_reconciler import ...` resolves (mirrors sibling external tests).\n- [ ] test_pydantic_text_mode runs the text path without tripping the snapshot gate (execution_mode='single_turn' — text needs no fs tools).\n- [ ] test_pydantic_review_code enables verify.enable_code_review and asserts the live gated path (runner == 'code-review-gate', findings is a list).\n- [ ] Verified end-to-end: the external-integration GitHub Action's external job runs green.","id":"8940-e719-61b3-4c4f","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"external suite: 3 live tests stale after post-06-16 design changes (unmasked by the ALLOW_MODEL_REQUESTS fix)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783652403099560001,"uuid":"c36fc090-f7e8-4043-9836-d39ab5d421cd"}